This paper analyzes the usage and citation data of a journal, which falls under the category of digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). It also examines the impact of papers, which could be related to cryptography (cs.CR), social and information networks (cs.SI), and computers and society (cs.CY).
